The paper deals with motion retargeting between humans and robots, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The use of deep reinforcement learning and optimization methods suggests that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of refined data in a latent space suggests that computer vision (cs.CV) may also be relevant. Finally, the mention of a human-in-the-loop approach suggests that the paper may also belong to the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
